**Edge Session UI Requirements**

**Becoming Protocol --- Arousal Session Interface**

**Executive Summary**

This document defines requirements for an immersive edging/gooning
interface that integrates with the existing Becoming Protocol systems:
arousal state tracking, Lovense haptic control, content tiering, arousal
auctions, and feminization conditioning.

The UI should feel like entering a distinct mode---immersive, focused,
psychologically compelling---while being functionally robust for
tracking, control, and post-session evidence capture.

**Part 1: Session Types & Entry Points**

**1.1 Session Type Definitions**

\| Type \| Purpose \| Frequency \| Duration \| Completion Allowed \|

\|\-\-\-\-\--\|\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\--\|\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\--\|\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\--\|\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\--\|

\| \*\*Type A: Anchoring\*\* \| Create feminization-arousal association
\| 2-3x weekly \| 20-40 min \| Denied (strengthens association) \|

\| \*\*Type B: Reward\*\* \| Positive reinforcement for practice \| 1x
weekly max \| 30-60 min \| Allowed (jackpot reward) \|

\| \*\*Type C: Maintenance\*\* \| Stay in sweet spot \| Daily option \|
10-20 min \| Denied \|

\| \*\*Goon Session\*\* \| Deep trance-like absorption \| Special unlock
\| 45-90 min \| Variable (AI decides) \|

**1.2 Entry Requirements**

interface SessionEntryRequirements { typeA: { available: \'always\',
requirements: \[\] }, typeB: { available: \'earned\', requirements: \[
\'weeklyProtocolComplete\', // All 7 days logged \'minDenialDays: 5\',
// At least 5 days since last release \'noActiveEdgeDebt\', // Edge debt
must be 0 \'noRecentTypeB: 7\' // At least 7 days since last Type B \]
}, typeC: { available: \'always\', requirements: \[\] }, goon: {
available: \'earned\', requirements: \[ \'phase: 3+\', // Phase 3 or
higher \'sessionCount: 20+\', // At least 20 sessions completed \'OR:
specialUnlock\' // Or specifically unlocked by system \] } }

**1.3 Entry Flow**

Today View → \"Begin Session\" button ↓ Session Type Selection (shows
availability, locked states) ↓ Pre-Session Check-In - Current arousal
state confirmation - Content tier unlocked display - Haptic device
connection check - Environment confirmation (\"Are you in a private
space?\") ↓ Session Configuration (for applicable types) - Target edges
(Type A/B) - AI control level - Content preferences - Time limit ↓
Session Start

