**3.2 Edge Data Capture**

interface EdgeEvent { id: string; sessionId: string; edgeNumber: number;
timestamp: Date; timeFromSessionStart: number; // seconds
timeSinceLastEdge: number; // seconds intensityAtEdge: number; // 0-20
(from haptic) hapticPatternActive: string; contentDisplayed?: string; //
ID of content shown auctionTriggered: boolean; notes?: string; }

**3.3 Recovery Period Tracking**

After each edge, brief recovery:

interface RecoveryPeriod { minDuration: 15, // seconds maxDuration: 60,
// seconds aiControlled: boolean, // AI decides when to resume display:
{ countdown: boolean, // Show timer (or hide for uncertainty)
breathingGuide: boolean, affirmationDuring: boolean, intensityDrop:
\'immediate\' \| \'gradual\' } }

