**Part 8: Session Completion Flow**

**8.1 Completion Types**

type CompletionType = \| \'denial\' // No release, session ends with
fadeout \| \'ruined\' // Ruined orgasm (partial reset) \| \'hands_free\'
// Hands-free orgasm (no reset!) \| \'full\' // Full release (Type B
only) \| \'emergency_stop\'; // User stopped early interface
CompletionConsequences { denial: { streakContinues: true,
edgeDebtCleared: false, bonusPoints: 50, affirmation: \"Good girl. You
held.\", nextSessionUnlock: \'immediate\' }, ruined: { streakResets:
true, edgeDebtAdded: 10, lockRequired: 24, // hours affirmation: \"Not
quite. She\'ll do better next time.\", cooldown: 24 // hours before next
session }, hands_free: { streakContinues: true, // KEY: Doesn\'t reset!
bonusPoints: 200, achievementUnlock: \'hands_free\', affirmation:
\"Perfect. She came the right way.\", nextSessionUnlock: \'immediate\'
}, full: { streakResets: true, requiresTypeB: true, // Only allowed in
Type B edgeDebtAdded: 20, lockRequired: 48, cooldown: 72, affirmation:
\"She earned this. Now rebuild.\" }, emergency_stop: { logged: true,
noConsequences: true, followUp: \'check_in_modal\' } }

**8.2 Denial Completion Flow**

Session nearing end (target edges reached or time limit) ↓ AI signals
wind-down - Intensity gradually decreases - Affirmations shift to
closure - \"You\'re almost done\... hold just a little longer\...\" ↓
Final edge (optional) ↓ Fadeout sequence - Intensity to 0 over 30
seconds - Breathing guide appears - \"Good girl. You held.\" ↓ Cool-down
period (2-3 minutes) - No haptics - Soft ambient content - Breathing
exercises - Gentle affirmations ↓ Post-session reflection modal

**8.3 Release Flow (Type B Only)**

User signals approaching climax ↓ AI confirmation: \"Type B session.
Release is permitted.\" ↓ Intensity escalation - Haptic pattern:
\'rewardClimb\' - Affirmations: \"You\'ve earned this\... let go\...\" -
Content: Peak tier unlocked ↓ Climax - User signals completion - Haptic
pattern: \'completion_pulse\' - \"Good girl. You earned this.\" ↓
Aftercare sequence - Gentle comedown - Extended affirmations - Soft
content - \"Rest now. She did well.\" ↓ Post-session logging

